    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏上美味之旅，轻松掌握日语假名与词汇！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《寿司学日文》是一款专为初学者打造的日语学习游戏，将日本回转寿司与扭蛋文化的乐趣结合，通过快节奏、互动性强的方式，帮助玩家轻松学会平假名、片假名，以及基础日语词汇（包含汉字）。本作采用怀旧像素风格，在PC端带来沉浸式的迷你游戏体验，让你在游戏中轻松入门日语！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ <strong>特色玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/b496909dd69043505d278776b029a2f9.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/b496909dd69043505d278776b029a2f9.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/b496909dd69043505d278776b029a2f9.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/f1f5854e550f7dd315e00e42933cfe31.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/f1f5854e550f7dd315e00e42933cfe31.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/f1f5854e550f7dd315e00e42933cfe31.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/12acd4500128ec17f52105b4e4dd1b13.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/12acd4500128ec17f52105b4e4dd1b13.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/12acd4500128ec17f52105b4e4dd1b13.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍣 <strong>寿司游戏</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回转寿司挑战</strong>：根据传送带上的寿司的平假名、片假名，输入或点击对应的罗马拼音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>猫顾客点单模式</strong>：聆听猫顾客的点餐语音，选择其假名与语音匹配的寿司</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寿司盒分类</strong>：将带有汉字或假名的寿司与对应的词义、图片进行配对</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扭蛋机惊喜</strong>：使用游戏内硬币扭蛋机，解锁更多新词汇与趣味内容！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📖 <strong>记忆辅助字典</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/76104ef8045d1deaf74bba91268cd535.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/76104ef8045d1deaf74bba91268cd535.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/76104ef8045d1deaf74bba91268cd535.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/e01c23d0bb4ec5e56bd0849b4d4d668b.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/e01c23d0bb4ec5e56bd0849b4d4d668b.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/e01c23d0bb4ec5e56bd0849b4d4d668b.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置<strong>联想记忆字典（英文版）及汉字对应表（中文版）</strong>，通过有趣的图像和故事，帮助你快速掌握假名发音与字形。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏅 <strong>适合 N5-N3 等级学习者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择适合自己的词汇范围，从入门级（N5）到中级（N3），自由调整学习进度。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 <strong>自定义游戏模式</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据个人学习需求，调整游戏速度与难度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择特定假名或词汇范围，集中学习不熟悉的部分。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎧 <strong>互动式日语发音</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配合日语发音，让你在游戏中聆听、认读假名与词汇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视觉与听觉双重学习，记忆更牢固！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎌 <strong>结合趣味与学习，让日语变得简单又好玩！</strong><br>无论你是日语初学者，还是想通过轻松的方式加强词汇记忆，《寿司学日文》都能让你在享受游戏的同时轻松积累日语实力！🎮✨</p>",
